## Jail judgment percentages\
\
What do monthly "CREDIT TIME SERVED" judgment percentages look like from January 2016 to November 20 2025?\
\
Making object:\
\
```\{r\}\
mo_jail_pct <- unhoused |> \
  filter(!is.na(whitmire_judgment)) |>\
  group_by(jud_yr,\
           jud_floor_mo, \
           whitmire_judgment) |> \
  summarise(jail_count = sum(judgment == "CREDIT TIME SERVED"),\
            total = n(),\
            jail_pct = round((jail_count/total)*100, 2)\
            ) |> \
  arrange(jud_floor_mo)\
\
mo_jail_pct\
```\
\
Plotting:\
\
```\{r\}\
mo_jail_pct_plot <- ggplot(\
  mo_jail_pct, \
  aes(x = jud_floor_mo, \
      y = jail_pct, \
